ts{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}], "milestone": null, "comments": 3, "created_at": "2016-12-28T23:16:55Z", "updated_at": "2016-12-29T20:22:22Z", "closed_at": "2016-12-29T20:22:22Z", "author_association": "MEMBER", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "This is a tracking issue for the tasks to revert `cargo check` and `--crate-type=metadata` in the Rust 1.15 release branch. currently `--crate-type=metadata` is on the `beta` branch of this repository and `cargo check` is itself in the rust-1.15.0 branch of the Cargo repository.\r\n\r\nUnfortunately there have been a number of bugs associated with `cargo check` since first implemented:\r\n\r\n* https://github.com/rust-lang/cargo/issues/3461\r\n* https://github.com/rust-lang/cargo/issues/3464\r\n* https://github.com/rust-lang/cargo/issues/3418\r\n* https://github.com/rust-lang/cargo/issues/3421\r\n* https://github.com/rust-lang/cargo/issues/3419\r\n* https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/38273\r\n\r\nAll of these issues, however, should be fixed by these two changes:\r\n\r\n* https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/38571\r\n* https://github.com/rust-lang/cargo/pull/3426\r\n\r\nWe need to fix the issues on beta in one way or another, and today the tools team decided to go ahead and revert the changes on beta and let the bug fixes ride the trains to stable in the Rust 1.16 release. There's two things that need to happen to close out this issue:\r\n\r\n* [x] Don't accept `--crate-type=metadata` in the compiler - https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/38668\r\n* [x] Remove the `cargo check` command from Cargo - https://github.com/rust-lang/cargo/pull/3465\r\n\r\n", "closed_by": {"login": "alexcrichton", "id": 64996, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjY0OTk2", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/64996?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton", "html_url": "https://github.com/alexcrichton", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/alexcrichton/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/38666/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/38666/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": "completed"}